The paper deals with the problem of minimizing edge crossings in geometric embeddings of graphs, which is a central topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper also involves algorithms and complexity analysis (cs.DS, cs.CC), as well as combinatorial optimization (cs.DM) and graph theory (cs.GT).
